SAP FICO/ABAP Consultant
SAP FICO/ABAP Consultant
Location:  Singapore
SAP FICO/ABAP Consultant- Permanent- Singapore
Amoria Bond Singapore is helping a major SAP in house user to fill a SAP FICO Consultant role based in Singapore. The ideal candidate needs to be able to perform complex business functional requirements analysis, systems specifications and design for business partners which are using SAP Applications.
Job Description:
- Provide project implementation and support on SAP modules such as FI/CO & ABAP application area
- Provide assistance in the development and provide analysis of SAP and business process problems and opportunities
- Evaluate, handle and resolve business problems, concerning SAP business processes, in such a way that the problems are always registered, confirmed to the business, carried out within the expected time frame according to the agreed budget
- Design detailed business and, wherever possible, technical specifications to programming and other resources, both in house and 3rd party
- Provide analysis of SAP and business processes problems and recommend application solutions to SAP Roll out implementation for FI/CO Module
- Apply local configuration on changing, fine tuning on SAP Settings and writing of specifications and performing programming
- Required to travel frequently to support/communicate with users across the regions
Requirements:
- IT/IS related degree
- 2-5 years or above with not less than 2 End to End implementations
- SAP/ Oracle/ Java or web base technology/ IT Project management
- SAP ERP6 (either functional or technical skill : eg FICO & ABAP)
- Negotiation & Presentation Skill, Communication & people interaction skills
- Mandarin speaking is mandatory
- Able to travel frequently to South East Asia countries
Please all interested candidates forward a copy of there CV to michelle.hoangcv@amoriabond.com.sg
for immediate interview.
Amoria Bond operates as an employment agency and employment business. No terminology in this advert is intended to discriminate on the grounds of age, and we confirm that we are happy to accept applications from persons of any age for this role.
